data.description: This home offers plenty of space with 3 bedrooms, 2 baths all on one level. Perfect for anyone. It is situated on over an acre of land so upkeep is easy. There is a beautiful pond in the back yard near the property line that is great for fishing. Sit on the screened in sun porch and admire the gorgeous view of the pond or the deer running and playing. Located near Grayson Highlands Park, Whitetop Mountain, hiking, biking you name it there is plenty to do and if you just want to relax that works too. Picturesque mountain views and abundant wildlife. You can walk into your master bath and within a few steps you have your enclosed hot tub room, this terrific hot tub is already and place and conveys with the property, This one is ready and waiting for you to call it home or your mountain getaway. Well maintained with hemlock siding. Breathtaking rock fireplace layed by the owner. Below tax value!!
